title: Safari Books Online
description: Use Safari Books Online to access e-books covering all aspects of computer science and information technology, including certification, computer science, databases, desktop applications, human-computer interaction, IT management, markup languages, networking, operating systems, programming, security, and software engineering. Publishers represented include O'Reilly, Prentice Hall, Addison-Wesley, Sams, Manning, Cisco Press, and SAS Publishing.
